      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "379-428",
      "markText": "我第一次看到特里·伦诺克斯时，他正坐在“舞者”俱乐部露台外的一辆劳斯莱斯“银色幽灵”里，喝得大醉。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40317513&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=379&rangeEnd=428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33c32c207267324933c162d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=379&rangeEnd=428"
    },
    {
