      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "605-647",
      "markText": "她的肩上披着一件蓝色貂皮大衣，几乎要使劳斯莱斯黯然失色了。还差一点，没东西真能做到。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40317513&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=605&rangeEnd=647",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/33c32c207267324933c162d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=605&rangeEnd=647"
